</ul>
<p><a href="/wiki/Langston_Hughes" title="Langston Hughes">Langston Hughes</a>'s autobiography also documents their meeting in <a href="/wiki/Turkestan" title="Turkestan">Turkestan</a> during the <a href="/wiki/Soviet" title="Soviet" class="mw-redirect">Soviet</a> era.</p>
<p><a name="Notes" id="Notes"></a></p>
<h2><span class="editsection">[<a href="/w/index.php?title=Arthur_Koestler&amp;action=edit&amp;section=20" title="Edit section: Notes">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline">Notes</span></h2>
<div class="references-small references-column-count references-column-count-2" style="-moz-column-count:2; column-count:2;">
